WEBVTT

1
00:00:38.499 --> 00:00:40.402
[♪ adventurous music plays]

2
00:00:48.705 --> 00:00:49.741
[Lo'ak] Come on. Bro.

3
00:00:50.748 --> 00:00:51.974
[laughs]

4
00:00:52.786 --> 00:00:55.747
Whoo! Whoo. whoo. whoo!

5
00:00:56.249 --> 00:00:57.419
[chuckles]

6
00:01:04.829 --> 00:01:06.560
Whoo! [chuckles]

7
00:01:07.161 --> 00:01:08.661
[Lo'ak ululates]

8
00:01:10.603 --> 00:01:11.701
Whoo!

9
00:01:11.836 --> 00:01:13.571
Whoa. Whoa.

10
00:01:13.707 --> 00:01:14.639
Hey. watch it.

11
00:01:14.775 --> 00:01:16.508
You were in my way. Bro.

12
00:01:16.643 --> 00:01:18.069
Oh. okay.

13
00:01:18.572 --> 00:01:21.113
-[Lo'ak] Whoo--
-[shrieks]

14
00:01:24.045 --> 00:01:25.447
Whoo!

15
00:01:26.685 --> 00:01:27.581
[grunts]

16
00:01:29.413 --> 00:01:30.617
Whoo!

17
00:01:32.119 --> 00:01:33.453
Whoo!

18
00:01:33.588 --> 00:01:35.024
[chuckles]
Is that all you got?

19
00:01:35.159 --> 00:01:37.492
You want to go faster. huh?

20
00:01:45.234 --> 00:01:47.535
[chuckles] Whoo-hoo!

21
00:01:50.637 --> 00:01:53.744
-[both panting]
-[ikran squawk]

22
00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:55.173
That was cool. Bro.

23
00:01:55.676 --> 00:01:57.545
[chuckles]<i> Skxawng</i> . let go.

24
00:02:00.550 --> 00:02:01.883
It was cool riding
with you. Bro.

25
00:02:02.018 --> 00:02:03.452
High four.

26
00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:04.856
[sighs]

27
00:02:04.992 --> 00:02:06.620
-[scoffs]
-[chuckles]

28
00:02:09.486 --> 00:02:11.392
[sighs]

29
00:02:11.527 --> 00:02:13.495
All right.
I got to get back. Bro.

30
00:02:14.162 --> 00:02:15.523
Little Brother.

31
00:02:16.026 --> 00:02:18.269
tell me one thing
before you go.

32
00:02:20.741 --> 00:02:22.141
How did I die?

33
00:02:28.639 --> 00:02:30.239
You got shot.

34
00:02:31.409 --> 00:02:33.977
We could have escaped. but I
made us go back for Spider.

35
00:02:34.921 --> 00:02:36.386
Then we had to go back.

36
00:02:37.022 --> 00:02:37.953
That's not your fault.

37
00:02:38.088 --> 00:02:39.218
Tell that to Dad.

38
00:02:39.688 --> 00:02:42.161
We weren't even supposed
to be out there.

39
00:02:43.297 --> 00:02:46.095
I got us caught
because I disobeyed orders.

40
00:02:46.230 --> 00:02:48.299
That's just you. Little Bro.

41
00:02:58.406 --> 00:03:00.135
I love you. Brother.

42
00:03:00.604 --> 00:03:01.642
<i> Skxawng.</i>

43
00:03:07.318 --> 00:03:09.210
[Lo'ak]<i> I killed my brother.</i>

44
00:03:09.880 --> 00:03:11.055
<i> No matter what happens.</i>

45
00:03:11.658 --> 00:03:15.392
<i> I have to live with that</i>
<i> for the rest of my life.</i>

46
00:03:44.483 --> 00:03:47.490
[panting]

47
00:03:53.758 --> 00:03:54.864
I wish I could do it.

48
00:03:55.266 --> 00:03:57.533
No. I wish I could do it.

49
00:03:58.901 --> 00:04:01.672
If I have another
stupid seizure underwater...

50
00:04:01.807 --> 00:04:02.865
Yeah.

51
00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:04.600
you'd be me
without a mask.

52
00:04:04.735 --> 00:04:06.870
[imitates choking]

53
00:04:07.006 --> 00:04:08.211
-Uh. let's test that.
-Hey. hey.

54
00:04:08.347 --> 00:04:09.814
-Watch it.
-See what happens.

55
00:04:09.950 --> 00:04:11.274
Hey. watch the stitches.

56
00:04:12.144 --> 00:04:13.909
Uh-huh. Yeah.
how do you like that. huh?

57
00:04:14.045 --> 00:04:15.287
-No! Ow! [shrieks]
-[laughs]

58
00:04:20.556 --> 00:04:23.592
[♪ Neytiri singing in Na'vi]

59
00:04:37.968 --> 00:04:39.376
[Lo'ak]<i> The fire of hate</i>

60
00:04:39.512 --> 00:04:41.643
<i> leaves only</i>
<i> the ash of grief.</i>

61
00:04:43.379 --> 00:04:44.739
<i> My mother mourned</i>

62
00:04:44.875 --> 00:04:46.141
<i> the ancient way.</i>

63
00:04:46.543 --> 00:04:49.244
<i> singing her son's life</i>
<i> during the daily eclipse.</i>

64
00:04:50.754 --> 00:04:53.083
<i> Because the light</i>
<i> always returns.</i>

65
00:04:59.624 --> 00:05:00.596
[singing fades]

66
00:05:02.292 --> 00:05:03.634
[Lo'ak]<i> There's the</i> Na'vi<i> way.</i>

67
00:05:04.404 --> 00:05:06.034
<i> and then there's</i>
<i> my dad's way.</i>

68
00:05:06.570 --> 00:05:09.308
<i> Say nothing.</i>
<i> Keep busy.</i>

69
00:05:10.702 --> 00:05:14.071
[breathes heavily]

70
00:05:24.221 --> 00:05:25.456
[ilu shrieks]

71
00:05:27.718 --> 00:05:30.362
[Lo'ak]<i> The Reef People say</i>
<i> the sea washes you clean.</i>

72
00:05:31.526 --> 00:05:33.061
<i> Washes away your sins.</i>

73
00:05:33.197 --> 00:05:34.564
[ilu squeaks]

74
00:06:10.167 --> 00:06:11.403
What do you got?

75
00:06:12.835 --> 00:06:14.236
You're supposed
to be collecting guns.

76
00:06:14.371 --> 00:06:16.133
That thing's useless.

77
00:06:16.602 --> 00:06:17.739
Focus. boy.

78
00:06:23.274 --> 00:06:25.208
Don't let your mother
see that.

79
00:06:34.026 --> 00:06:35.017
Hey. excuse me.

80
00:06:35.152 --> 00:06:36.325
-Sorry. [laughs]
-Excuse me.

81
00:06:36.460 --> 00:06:37.990
-Tuk.
-[Tuk] Sorry.

82
00:06:44.838 --> 00:06:46.064
Bro.

83
00:06:47.534 --> 00:06:48.770
Ah. sick.

84
00:06:50.076 --> 00:06:51.300
What is this?

85
00:06:52.472 --> 00:06:53.511
Tsireya?

86
00:06:54.873 --> 00:06:56.371
What are you doing?

87
00:06:58.416 --> 00:07:00.716
This is an AR. all right?

88
00:07:00.852 --> 00:07:03.018
This is the mag.
It's where the bullets are.

89
00:07:03.153 --> 00:07:04.522
Empty.

90
00:07:05.419 --> 00:07:06.458
Slap it.

91
00:07:07.388 --> 00:07:08.090
Rack it.

92
00:07:08.225 --> 00:07:09.587
And then. boom.

93
00:07:09.723 --> 00:07:11.222
you can just spray.

94
00:07:11.358 --> 00:07:12.887
[chuckles] You can kill
a lot of Sky People with this.

95
00:07:13.023 --> 00:07:14.829
See? Ceramic action.

96
00:07:14.965 --> 00:07:17.125
You clean 'em and oil 'em.
be as good as new.

97
00:07:17.260 --> 00:07:19.200
This is not the<i> Na'vi</i> way.

98
00:07:19.336 --> 00:07:20.370
<i> Jakesully.</i>

99
00:07:20.505 --> 00:07:22.698
Weapons of metal
are forbidden.

100
00:07:22.834 --> 00:07:23.765
You know this.

101
00:07:23.901 --> 00:07:24.833
To touch them

102
00:07:24.968 --> 00:07:26.511
poisons the heart.

103
00:07:26.913 --> 00:07:27.835
Eywa

104
00:07:27.971 --> 00:07:29.239
will provide.

105
00:07:29.742 --> 00:07:31.640
[sighs] Right.

106
00:07:32.443 --> 00:07:34.818
The mourning period
is not even over.

107
00:07:34.954 --> 00:07:36.147
Tuk.

108
00:07:36.282 --> 00:07:37.221
[Ronal] You should be
with your family.

109
00:07:37.356 --> 00:07:38.956
not gathering these things.

110
00:07:39.091 --> 00:07:40.617
Your woman

111
00:07:40.752 --> 00:07:42.087
needs you.

112
00:07:43.696 --> 00:07:47.125
My son lies with the ancestors
in the reef.

113
00:07:47.826 --> 00:07:49.167
This is our home.

114
00:07:49.302 --> 00:07:51.128
I said I would stand and fight.

115
00:07:51.264 --> 00:07:53.961
but I can't fight gunships
with spears.

116
00:07:54.097 --> 00:07:55.899
We sank the demon ship.

117
00:07:56.034 --> 00:07:58.070
The pink skins fear us now.

118
00:07:59.344 --> 00:08:01.245
Yeah? We got lucky.

119
00:08:01.381 --> 00:08:03.174
And they got many more ships.

120
00:08:03.777 --> 00:08:05.311
Least we got these.

121
00:08:06.247 --> 00:08:08.752
We are grateful you
stand with us.<i> Jakesully.</i>

122
00:08:09.255 --> 00:08:10.650
It is not guns we need.

123
00:08:10.785 --> 00:08:12.348
It is Rider of Last Shadow.

124
00:08:13.951 --> 00:08:15.587
Ride great<i> toruk</i>

125
00:08:15.722 --> 00:08:17.787
as you did before.

126
00:08:18.290 --> 00:08:22.166
[inhales deeply]
When you ride the beast.

127
00:08:22.301 --> 00:08:23.997
you become the beast.

128
00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:27.297
And the more blood.
the better.

129
00:08:28.801 --> 00:08:30.636
I will not become

130
00:08:30.772 --> 00:08:32.775
<i> Toruk Makto</i> again.

131
00:08:33.773 --> 00:08:35.140
<i> Jakesully.</i>

132
00:08:35.910 --> 00:08:38.209
you are always<i> Toruk Makto.</i>

133
00:08:39.118 --> 00:08:41.377
Come. Rotxo.

134
00:08:46.886 --> 00:08:47.951
<i> Can you hear me?</i>

135
00:08:48.420 --> 00:08:49.719
[Scoresby] Yeah. we can
hear you loud and clear.

136
00:08:49.854 --> 00:08:50.889
Go on. Doc.

137
00:08:51.592 --> 00:08:54.724
<i> So. uh. we've been through</i>
<i> the wreck. inside and out.</i>

138
00:08:54.860 --> 00:08:58.226
<i> Uh. we've searched to about</i>
<i> a 200-meter radius around it.</i>

139
00:08:58.629 --> 00:09:00.165
<i> We didn't find</i>
<i> any</i> Na'vi<i> bodies.</i>

140
00:09:00.300 --> 00:09:03.241
<i> Just crew or...</i>
<i> what's left of 'em.</i>

141
00:09:03.376 --> 00:09:05.535
Well. keep looking. Doctor.

142
00:09:05.671 --> 00:09:07.969
-Expand the search radius.
-[Dr. Garvin]<i> Roger that.</i>

143
00:09:08.104 --> 00:09:09.438
<i> Of note though.</i>

144
00:09:09.574 --> 00:09:11.242
<i> I did find an interesting</i>
<i> new algae.</i>

145
00:09:12.847 --> 00:09:14.379
<i> Hello? Can you hear me?</i>

146
00:09:14.515 --> 00:09:16.346
-Sully is still out there.
-[Ardmore] We don't know that.

147
00:09:16.481 --> 00:09:18.684
Scavengers could have
carried off the bodies.

148
00:09:18.819 --> 00:09:20.924
Nope. He made it out.

149
00:09:21.059 --> 00:09:24.528
And he's in this area.
Down to a handful of villages.

150
00:09:24.663 --> 00:09:26.163
You just give me a ship
and I'll--

151
00:09:26.298 --> 00:09:27.365
I gave you a ship.

152
00:09:27.501 --> 00:09:29.460
It's right there.
on the bottom.

153
00:09:30.029 --> 00:09:31.603
Yeah. Along with my crew.

154
00:09:32.435 --> 00:09:33.462
All dead.

155
00:09:34.241 --> 00:09:35.965
You brought me out here.

156
00:09:36.101 --> 00:09:38.066
twenty-six trillion miles.

157
00:09:38.201 --> 00:09:39.837
for a single mission.

158
00:09:39.972 --> 00:09:41.507
a kinetic hard kill op

159
00:09:41.642 --> 00:09:43.673
against one guy.

160
00:09:44.042 --> 00:09:46.211
I ain't backing off.

161
00:09:49.514 --> 00:09:52.019
[Dr. Garvin]
<i> Are we still connected? Hello?</i>

162
00:09:52.887 --> 00:09:54.593
<i> Do they have me on mute?</i>

163
00:10:01.295 --> 00:10:04.031
The spirit of my ancestors
is in this bow.

164
00:10:06.163 --> 00:10:07.562
It was our strength.

165
00:10:10.467 --> 00:10:13.271
I can help you
fix it. Lo'ak.

166
00:10:14.806 --> 00:10:16.043
No!

167
00:10:16.974 --> 00:10:18.279
It's ruined!

168
00:10:19.215 --> 00:10:21.444
[Lo'ak]<i> Everything I touch</i>
<i> gets ruined.</i>

169
00:10:26.317 --> 00:10:28.154
<i> They never talked about it.</i>

170
00:10:29.762 --> 00:10:31.557
<i> But it was there</i>
<i> in the room.</i>

171
00:10:32.026 --> 00:10:33.854
<i> Like a crouching thanator.</i>

172
00:10:33.990 --> 00:10:35.425
[sighs]

173
00:10:37.133 --> 00:10:39.462
I know you will never
give up your bow.

174
00:10:41.437 --> 00:10:42.465
So...

175
00:10:47.142 --> 00:10:49.175
Just don't be close
when it hits.

176
00:10:52.514 --> 00:10:54.218
[sighs]

177
00:10:54.354 --> 00:10:57.117
[breathing shakily]

178
00:11:07.764 --> 00:11:10.130
So. you agree with Ronal?

179
00:11:13.531 --> 00:11:15.371
I will never speak against
my husband

180
00:11:15.507 --> 00:11:17.335
in front of that woman.

181
00:11:19.808 --> 00:11:21.207
Look. I'm a marine.

182
00:11:22.749 --> 00:11:25.046
I'm not taking a knife
to a gunfight.

183
00:11:26.980 --> 00:11:28.313
Or a prayer. [scoffs]

184
00:11:30.623 --> 00:11:32.614
So. what am I
supposed to do?

185
00:11:33.450 --> 00:11:36.257
I can't run.
I can't fight.

186
00:11:36.626 --> 00:11:37.625
Oh. that's right.

187
00:11:38.161 --> 00:11:41.092
Eywa will provide. Yeah?
So. where was Eywa?

188
00:11:41.228 --> 00:11:42.924
Where was Eywa
when our son--

189
00:11:43.059 --> 00:11:44.296
Jake!

190
00:11:46.598 --> 00:11:49.466
I'm in this place
where I have nothing.

191
00:11:50.402 --> 00:11:53.338
Not my people.
not my forest.

192
00:11:54.471 --> 00:11:56.638
Even my father's bow
is gone.

193
00:11:59.583 --> 00:12:00.719
All I have...

194
00:12:01.914 --> 00:12:03.352
is my faith

195
00:12:03.988 --> 00:12:06.552
that this is
the Great Mother's plan.

196
00:12:06.921 --> 00:12:09.151
[breathing shakily]

197
00:12:09.286 --> 00:12:11.191
You have this family.

198
00:12:25.135 --> 00:12:26.635
And you have me.

199
00:12:28.844 --> 00:12:31.013
And I love you so much.

200
00:12:35.188 --> 00:12:37.756
[sobs]

201
00:12:40.293 --> 00:12:43.451
[chittering]

202
00:12:43.586 --> 00:12:45.460
[♪ adventurous music plays]

203
00:12:45.595 --> 00:12:46.721
[bellows]

204
00:12:52.635 --> 00:12:54.065
[whistles]

205
00:12:54.201 --> 00:12:56.372
Yeah. Payakan.
you're the man!

206
00:12:56.507 --> 00:12:59.008
[rumbles]

207
00:13:03.142 --> 00:13:05.377
[tulkun vocalizing]

208
00:13:23.699 --> 00:13:24.726
Whoa. Bro. Bro.

209
00:13:25.162 --> 00:13:26.398
[exclaims]

210
00:13:27.903 --> 00:13:30.534
This is sick! [laughs]

211
00:13:32.503 --> 00:13:34.769
-Whoo! Whoo!
-Whoo-hoo!

212
00:13:36.744 --> 00:13:38.344
Whoo!

213
00:13:40.851 --> 00:13:43.118
-[laughs]
-[screams]

214
00:13:44.749 --> 00:13:46.783
-Whoo! [laughs]
-Bro. come on! Go. go. go. go!

215
00:13:47.319 --> 00:13:49.388
-Oh. sh...
-Yeah!

216
00:13:54.259 --> 00:13:55.861
That was insane. cuz.

217
00:13:55.997 --> 00:13:57.363
I know. right. Bro?

218
00:13:58.162 --> 00:13:59.128
[Tsireya laughs]

219
00:13:59.264 --> 00:14:00.632
I thought you were dead.

220
00:14:01.201 --> 00:14:03.538
[both imitate splash. laugh]

221
00:14:04.340 --> 00:14:07.008
It sucks that Payakan
is still an outcast.

222
00:14:07.144 --> 00:14:08.908
Yeah. After saving
all our asses.

223
00:14:09.043 --> 00:14:10.476
No.
I'm sorry.

224
00:14:10.611 --> 00:14:12.713
but by the<i> tulkun</i> way.
he bears the deaths.

225
00:14:12.848 --> 00:14:13.949
[Payakan rumbling]

226
00:14:14.084 --> 00:14:15.414
All those
who died in the battle.

227
00:14:16.116 --> 00:14:17.647
He bears those deaths.

228
00:14:19.549 --> 00:14:22.586
I'm sorry. You saved us all.

229
00:14:23.088 --> 00:14:24.621
[rumbling]

230
00:14:29.131 --> 00:14:30.862
[distorted] Forever. Brother.

231
00:14:30.997 --> 00:14:31.929
[normal] Always.

232
00:14:32.064 --> 00:14:34.136
[bellows]

233
00:14:37.840 --> 00:14:41.044
[exo-pack beeping]

234
00:14:41.679 --> 00:14:43.574
[gasping. choking]

235
00:14:45.010 --> 00:14:46.247
Dad!

236
00:14:49.982 --> 00:14:51.852
-Wait. where's the spare?
-It's in the basket. I think.

237
00:14:51.988 --> 00:14:53.186
Hey! Wake up! Where is it?

238
00:14:53.322 --> 00:14:54.817
-Hey! Where's the spare mask?
-What?

239
00:14:54.953 --> 00:14:56.826
Where's the spare mask?
Used to be there. Where is it?

240
00:14:56.961 --> 00:14:58.258
-I don't know.
-Find it.

241
00:14:58.394 --> 00:14:59.822
-It's not here.
-Speak to me. Where is it?

242
00:14:59.958 --> 00:15:02.098
-[Kiri] I can't find it.
-[Jake] Hey. hey! Where is it?

243
00:15:02.233 --> 00:15:03.796
-Come on. Come on. Come on.
-I got it. Dad.

244
00:15:04.199 --> 00:15:06.135
-Dad. I found it.
-Hurry.

245
00:15:08.166 --> 00:15:09.367
[beeping stops]

246
00:15:09.503 --> 00:15:10.935
-[breathing heavily]
-[air hisses]

247
00:15:11.070 --> 00:15:12.770
Spider. no.

248
00:15:12.906 --> 00:15:13.842
Breathe.

249
00:15:13.977 --> 00:15:15.843
-Breathe.
-Breathe.

250
00:15:15.978 --> 00:15:17.476
[Jake] Deep and slow.

251
00:15:17.979 --> 00:15:19.109
Deep and slow.

252
00:15:19.511 --> 00:15:21.118
There you go.
You're okay.

253
00:15:21.253 --> 00:15:24.384
[breathing deeply] I'm good.
I'm good. I'm okay.

254
00:15:26.289 --> 00:15:28.418
<i> Skxawng.</i>
You have to be careful.

255
00:15:28.820 --> 00:15:30.390
-Careful's my middle name.
-Yeah.<i> skxawng.</i>

256
00:15:30.525 --> 00:15:32.022
You should be more careful.
little baby.

257
00:15:32.158 --> 00:15:33.692
Pay attention.

258
00:15:33.828 --> 00:15:35.923
-Get off. Get off. Get off.
