Oh.

1069
00:59:29.566 --> 00:59:31.395
Yeah. I'm good
on the whole air thing.

1070
00:59:31.764 --> 00:59:34.229
[♪ majestic music plays]

1071
00:59:38.471 --> 00:59:39.565
[shrieks]

1072
00:59:40.067 --> 00:59:42.238
[gasps] Tuktirey.

1073
00:59:42.607 --> 00:59:44.107
[chuckles] Kiri.

1074
00:59:49.915 --> 00:59:51.415
Iron Sky.
Blue One actual.

1075
00:59:51.551 --> 00:59:52.483
We're inbound

1076
00:59:52.618 --> 00:59:54.051
at the city wall.

1077
00:59:54.718 --> 00:59:55.651
[music ends]

1078
00:59:55.786 --> 00:59:57.758
[machines beeping]

1079
01:00:05.130 --> 01:00:07.064
So. you think
he's still with Sully?

1080
01:00:07.832 --> 01:00:08.994
I'd make book on it.

1081
01:00:09.130 --> 01:00:11.033
This is not my priority.

1082
01:00:11.169 --> 01:00:13.442
My priority is getting
this city built

1083
01:00:13.577 --> 01:00:15.209
and sending back amrita
to pay for it.

1084
01:00:15.345 --> 01:00:16.368
And who do you think

1085
01:00:16.503 --> 01:00:17.804
sets your priorities.
General?

1086
01:00:18.306 --> 01:00:19.504
It's the
big-picture guys.

1087
01:00:19.639 --> 01:00:21.309
So here's a big-picture
concept for you.

1088
01:00:21.444 --> 01:00:23.112
How are we supposed
to colonize this world

1089
01:00:23.248 --> 01:00:24.776
if we can't breathe
the fricking air?

1090
01:00:25.412 --> 01:00:26.849
You want to
find the boy.

1091
01:00:26.985 --> 01:00:28.314
you got to
find Sully.

1092
01:00:28.449 --> 01:00:30.249
-And I'm there.
-[grunts] Ow. Ow.

1093
01:00:30.385 --> 01:00:31.653
How many more
of these. huh?

1094
01:00:31.789 --> 01:00:32.923
Not many more.

1095
01:00:33.059 --> 01:00:33.787
That's what
you said yesterday.

1096
01:00:33.922 --> 01:00:34.990
Don't be a baby.

1097
01:00:35.125 --> 01:00:35.955
Here's the most
recent scan.

1098
01:00:36.090 --> 01:00:37.089
Now. you see this?

1099
01:00:37.224 --> 01:00:38.565
This is all mycelium.

1100
01:00:38.701 --> 01:00:40.125
It's basically
the same thing

1101
01:00:40.260 --> 01:00:41.397
as the forest network.

1102
01:00:41.533 --> 01:00:42.467
Somehow.

1103
01:00:42.602 --> 01:00:43.471
it colonized him.

1104
01:00:43.607 --> 01:00:45.196
spread through
his entire system

1105
01:00:45.332 --> 01:00:46.531
and then
made changes

1106
01:00:46.666 --> 01:00:48.736
at the cellular level.
I mean. look.

1107
01:00:49.338 --> 01:00:51.073
It altered
his blood chemistry.

1108
01:00:51.208 --> 01:00:52.675
his nervous system.
his lungs.

1109
01:00:52.811 --> 01:00:54.177
Can you get it out?

1110
01:00:55.012 --> 01:00:56.409
No. it's an endosymbiont.

1111
01:00:56.545 --> 01:00:58.779
We think they're keeping
each other alive.

1112
01:00:59.315 --> 01:01:00.989
It could kill him
if we even try.

1113
01:01:01.525 --> 01:01:03.520
But look.
I mean. he's...

1114
01:01:03.655 --> 01:01:04.525
he's alive.

1115
01:01:04.661 --> 01:01:06.153
-He's healthy.
-[beatboxing]

1116
01:01:06.289 --> 01:01:07.687
Maybe this is
a good thing.

1117
01:01:08.056 --> 01:01:09.291
A good thing?

1118
01:01:11.101 --> 01:01:12.527
[sighs]

1119
01:01:12.996 --> 01:01:14.227
What if the RDA labs

1120
01:01:14.363 --> 01:01:15.897
could reverse
engineer this?

1121
01:01:16.300 --> 01:01:17.801
What if every human being
on Earth

1122
01:01:17.936 --> 01:01:19.833
could live here without a mask?

1123
01:01:19.968 --> 01:01:21.336
[clicks tongue]

1124
01:01:22.239 --> 01:01:25.509
Uh. Jake.
there's something else.

1125
01:01:25.645 --> 01:01:27.509
Sit. Hey. bud.

1126
01:01:27.645 --> 01:01:28.583
Hey.

1127
01:01:28.719 --> 01:01:30.180
-Okay. let me see.
-[Spider] Hey.

1128
01:01:30.315 --> 01:01:32.248
Hold-Hold still. Hold still.
You're fine.

1129
01:01:34.283 --> 01:01:35.619
-Look at that.
-[Spider grunts]

1130
01:01:35.755 --> 01:01:36.791
What are you doing?

1131
01:01:37.294 --> 01:01:38.250
What is that?

1132
01:01:38.385 --> 01:01:40.091
He's growin' a<i> kuru</i> .

1133
01:01:40.927 --> 01:01:43.193
-Wait. what?
-Oh. yeah.

1134
01:01:47.265 --> 01:01:50.002
[voices chanting.
speaking in Na'vi]

1135
01:01:55.972 --> 01:01:57.405
[voices stop]

1136
01:01:58.282 --> 01:01:59.638
Great Mother.

1137
01:02:00.845 --> 01:02:02.080
are you there?

1138
01:02:02.779 --> 01:02:03.842
Please.

1139
01:02:04.278 --> 01:02:06.282
Hear my small voice.

1140
01:02:08.350 --> 01:02:10.787
I prayed to you
in the forest

1141
01:02:10.922 --> 01:02:12.585
to save
my friend.

1142
01:02:13.286 --> 01:02:15.093
I prayed so hard.

1143
01:02:17.896 --> 01:02:19.262
But you didn't come.

1144
01:02:20.766 --> 01:02:22.029
You didn't answer.

1145
01:02:22.165 --> 01:02:25.004
So I had
to do it myself.

1146
01:02:25.805 --> 01:02:26.733
I don't know how I...

1147
01:02:26.869 --> 01:02:27.906
I...

1148
01:02:28.041 --> 01:02:30.042
I asked the roots
to help me.

1149
01:02:30.844 --> 01:02:32.407
I don't remember
how I--

1150
01:02:35.208 --> 01:02:36.615
Please. no.

1151
01:02:36.750 --> 01:02:38.479
No. don't shut me out.

1152
01:02:39.214 --> 01:02:40.679
Why am I like this?

1153
01:02:41.989 --> 01:02:44.089
How am I doing
these things?

1154
01:02:44.758 --> 01:02:46.718
Please. just talk to me.

1155
01:02:47.120 --> 01:02:48.357
Please.

1156
01:02:49.533 --> 01:02:51.492
No. no.
Please. please.

1157
01:02:52.160 --> 01:02:53.859
[sobs] No. No.

1158
01:02:53.995 --> 01:02:56.398
No. No!

1159
01:02:57.065 --> 01:02:59.170
[gasping]

1160
01:03:00.006 --> 01:03:01.667
[♪ mysterious music plays]

1161
01:03:02.741 --> 01:03:04.208
[grunting]

1162
01:03:05.711 --> 01:03:06.915
[birds chirping]

1163
01:03:07.050 --> 01:03:08.877
-[Norm] EEG is fine.
-[Jake] It's blinking. So--

1164
01:03:09.446 --> 01:03:10.714
That's blood pressure.
That's normal.

1165
01:03:10.850 --> 01:03:12.016
You want that blinking.

1166
01:03:12.152 --> 01:03:13.447
-Let's take these off.
-[Neytiri] Kiri.

1167
01:03:13.582 --> 01:03:16.488
-Run more tests.
-Eywa never came to me.

1168
01:03:16.623 --> 01:03:18.087
I told you.

1169
01:03:18.222 --> 01:03:20.051
I don't know
how I did it.

1170
01:03:20.186 --> 01:03:21.456
Drink.

1171
01:03:21.891 --> 01:03:22.892
Kiri.

1172
01:03:23.595 --> 01:03:27.429
My child. you are touched
by the All Mother's hand.

1173
01:03:28.296 --> 01:03:29.702
This we
have known

1174
01:03:29.837 --> 01:03:31.268
since you
were born.

1175
01:03:32.401 --> 01:03:34.370
[♪ pensive music playing]

1176
01:03:37.676 --> 01:03:38.972
[sighs]

1177
01:03:39.475 --> 01:03:41.575
There's something
you're hiding.

1178
01:03:42.078 --> 01:03:43.581
I have felt it

1179
01:03:43.717 --> 01:03:44.682
my whole life.

1180
01:03:44.818 --> 01:03:46.945
Just tell me the truth.

1181
01:03:47.081 --> 01:03:48.318
Please.

1182
01:03:49.986 --> 01:03:51.222
Tell her.

1183
01:03:53.825 --> 01:03:55.127
It is time.

1184
01:03:57.730 --> 01:03:58.757
My child.

1185
01:04:00.634 --> 01:04:01.661
You do not

1186
01:04:02.803 --> 01:04:04.667
have a father. Kiri.

1187
01:04:04.802 --> 01:04:06.039
What?

1188
01:04:06.573 --> 01:04:07.232
You...

1189
01:04:07.368 --> 01:04:08.705
Your... Your mother.

1190
01:04:08.840 --> 01:04:10.070
Grace's avatar.

1191
01:04:10.472 --> 01:04:12.006
now.
when she was pregnant.

1192
01:04:12.142 --> 01:04:13.275
Norm ran some tests.

1193
01:04:13.410 --> 01:04:14.811
And it was a path...
pathelo--

1194
01:04:14.947 --> 01:04:16.782
A-A parthenogenic birth.

1195
01:04:17.284 --> 01:04:19.852
You're genetically identical
to the avatar.

1196
01:04:19.987 --> 01:04:22.220
There literally
is no father.

1197
01:04:23.123 --> 01:04:25.157
[breathes shakily]
I'm a clone?

1198
01:04:26.287 --> 01:04:27.386
Granddaughter.

1199
01:04:27.521 --> 01:04:30.096
It was the will
of Eywa.

1200
01:04:32.100 --> 01:04:34.461
When the dreamwalker body
lay here

1201
01:04:34.596 --> 01:04:37.334
in the Great Mother's
hands...

1202
01:04:39.239 --> 01:04:41.767
[echoing]
...a seed was planted.

1203
01:04:44.472 --> 01:04:46.607
[♪ chanting in Na'vi]

1204
01:04:50.145 --> 01:04:51.546
[chanting stops]

1205
01:04:52.685 --> 01:04:54.016
[scoffs]

1206
01:04:54.151 --> 01:04:55.818
That really
sucks.

1207
01:04:56.487 --> 01:04:59.086
That makes me
even more of a freak.

1208
01:04:59.221 --> 01:05:01.562
No. granddaughter.

1209
01:05:01.697 --> 01:05:04.691
You are Eywa's child.

1210
01:05:06.666 --> 01:05:08.662
[sighs]

1211
01:05:10.904 --> 01:05:11.834
[Jake] I don't care

1212
01:05:11.969 --> 01:05:13.173
how it happened.

1213
01:05:14.009 --> 01:05:15.937
-[sighs]
-You're my baby girl.

1214
01:05:16.607 --> 01:05:19.409
And I'm the only father
you'll ever need.

1215
01:05:20.944 --> 01:05:22.478
[sighs]

1216
01:05:24.115 --> 01:05:25.514
If I am so special.

1217
01:05:27.518 --> 01:05:30.222
why does Eywa
fold her ears to me?

1218
01:05:33.025 --> 01:05:34.191
Look. we don't know why.

1219
01:05:34.327 --> 01:05:35.994
but you're locked out
from her.

1220
01:05:36.129 --> 01:05:37.324
It's some kind
of firewall.

1221
01:05:37.460 --> 01:05:38.558
Yeah. it's like
an encryption.

1222
01:05:38.693 --> 01:05:39.931
The harder
you try to break in.

1223
01:05:40.067 --> 01:05:41.563
the harder
it fights back.

1224
01:05:43.465 --> 01:05:44.905
Eywa has a path
for you.

1225
01:05:45.041 --> 01:05:47.239
Though she chooses
to conceal it.

1226
01:05:47.941 --> 01:05:49.844
you must trust in her.

1227
01:05:49.979 --> 01:05:51.845
I have to find out
what it is.

1228
01:05:51.980 --> 01:05:54.213
No. you have
to stop asking.

1229
01:05:55.551 --> 01:05:56.982
Kiri. if...

1230
01:05:57.118 --> 01:05:59.112
if you try
to connect again.

1231
01:05:59.248 --> 01:06:00.247
you could die.

1232
01:06:00.750 --> 01:06:03.453
You do it underwater.
and you will die.

1233
01:06:06.528 --> 01:06:07.590
[sighs]

1234
01:06:08.226 --> 01:06:09.960
[Jake] He can't stay here.

1235
01:06:10.095 --> 01:06:11.663
If the RDA get him...

1236
01:06:12.166 --> 01:06:14.035
well. we'll never
stop 'em.

1237
01:06:15.001 --> 01:06:16.836
If he is so dangerous.

1238
01:06:16.972 --> 01:06:19.040
to The People. to everything.

1239
01:06:19.940 --> 01:06:21.636
we should just kill him.

1240
01:06:25.209 --> 01:06:27.644
[chuckles] It's Spider.

1241
01:06:28.413 --> 01:06:30.385
He'll come with us.
He'll come

1242
01:06:30.520 --> 01:06:31.575
to the reef.

1243
01:06:31.711 --> 01:06:33.318
We can protect him there.

1244
01:06:34.956 --> 01:06:37.454
<i> Toruk Makto</i> knows best.

1245
01:06:38.089 --> 01:06:39.387
Oh. come on. baby.

1246
01:06:39.522 --> 01:06:41.062
-It's not like that.
-[sighs]

1247
01:06:41.697 --> 01:06:42.998
It is decided.

1248
01:06:54.538 --> 01:06:56.704
Thirty meters.
Get me up in there.

1249
01:07:03.082 --> 01:07:04.479
Get me in the pocket.

1250
01:07:04.615 --> 01:07:07.286
Get me in the pocket
with the rocket.

1251
01:07:07.821 --> 01:07:09.057
Ten meters.

1252
01:07:11.221 --> 01:07:13.292
Here we go. And...

1253
01:07:17.666 --> 01:07:18.726
[shrieks]

1254
01:07:25.069 --> 01:07:28.971
[bellows]

1255
01:07:29.106 --> 01:07:30.534
Lung shot.

1256
01:07:30.670 --> 01:07:32.003
She's bleeding out.

1257
01:07:33.539 --> 01:07:34.646
[tulkun shrieks]

1258
01:07:34.781 --> 01:07:36.117
Whoo!

1259
01:07:39.182 --> 01:07:41.320
[tulkun wailing]

1260
01:08:04.307 --> 01:08:05.842
[ikran screeches]

1261
01:08:06.345 --> 01:08:08.910
A new demon ship
has come.

1262
01:08:09.046 --> 01:08:10.580
Bigger.

1263
01:08:10.715 --> 01:08:12.618
More of our<i> tulkun</i>
have been killed.

1264
01:08:13.020 --> 01:08:14.454
I'm so sorry. Brother.

1265
01:08:14.823 --> 01:08:16.057
<i> Jakesully.</i>

1266
01:08:16.193 --> 01:08:18.520
the outcast is stirring up
the young bulls.

1267
01:08:18.656 --> 01:08:20.551
Our<i> tulkun</i>
have called for council

1268
01:08:20.687 --> 01:08:22.097
to decide about him.

1269
01:08:24.030 --> 01:08:25.265
You must rest.

1270
01:08:26.431 --> 01:08:28.765
This must be removed.
See me.

1271
01:08:29.167 --> 01:08:30.732
Kids. Kids. on me.

1272
01:08:33.037 --> 01:08:34.307
[groans]

1273
01:08:34.908 --> 01:08:36.408
[strains. wails]

1274
01:08:37.108 --> 01:08:39.213
[shouts. groans]

1275
01:08:40.540 --> 01:08:41.577
[Kiri chuckling]

1276
01:08:41.713 --> 01:08:43.446
No. I'm serious.
When it grows long enough.

1277
01:08:43.582 --> 01:08:45.047
I'm going to get
my own<i> ilu</i> .

1278
01:08:45.182 --> 01:08:46.812
<i> Skxawng.</i>

1279
01:08:46.947 --> 01:08:48.282
You need
a very small<i> ilu</i> .

1280
01:08:48.418 --> 01:08:49.551
[Spider] Just you watch.

1281
01:08:49.687 --> 01:08:51.225
I'm going to
get my own skimwing.

1282
01:08:51.361 --> 01:08:52.788
-Oh. a skimwing?
-Then I'll be the one laughing.

1283
01:08:53.157 --> 01:08:55.020
So. how is this?

1284
01:08:55.655 --> 01:08:56.555
Your daughter.

1285
01:08:56.691 --> 01:08:58.760
your half-blood daughter.

1286
01:09:00.199 --> 01:09:01.598
with no training...

1287
01:09:02.533 --> 01:09:03.996
-Hold here.
-[groans]

1288
01:09:04.131 --> 01:09:07.065
...has done what
no<i> Tsahik</i> could do?

1289
01:09:08.102 --> 01:09:10.601
Who are you to question
the will of Eywa?

1290
01:09:10.737 --> 01:09:11.844
I am<i> Tsahik</i> !

1291
01:09:11.980 --> 01:09:13.614
Then be<i> Tsahik</i> !

1292
01:09:14.083 --> 01:09:15.614
These herbs
do nothing!

1293
01:09:16.384 --> 01:09:18.747
Herbs from my forest
heal faster.

1294
01:09:19.922 --> 01:09:21.479
I tell you to rest.

1295
01:09:21.614 --> 01:09:22.924
You do not rest.

1296
01:09:23.059 --> 01:09:25.325
Then you blame
my herbs.

1297
01:09:26.729 --> 01:09:27.756
Hold still.

1298
01:09:28.631 --> 01:09:30.422
[groans]

1299
01:09:30.558 --> 01:09:31.766
Stupid woman.

1300
01:09:31.902 --> 01:09:33.194
Careful.<i> Tsahik</i> .

1301
01:09:33.329 --> 01:09:34.735
or I may forget

1302
01:09:34.871 --> 01:09:36.134
that you are with child.

1303
01:09:36.269 --> 01:09:39.174
-[snarls]
-[snarls]

1304
01:09:41.072 --> 01:09:42.309
[scoffs]

1305
01:09:47.542 --> 01:09:49.580
[tulkun rumbling]

1306
01:09:57.216 --> 01:09:58.983
[Tonowari]
The matriarch has spoken.

1307
01:09:59.118 --> 01:10:01.455
She says the outcast
continues

1308
01:10:01.591 --> 01:10:03.661
to defy the<i> tulkun</i> way.

1309
01:10:04.297 --> 01:10:06.033
All killing is forbidden.

1310
01:10:06.168 --> 01:10:07.793
He was outcast
for this.

1311
01:10:07.928 --> 01:10:10.001
but he has
done it again.

1312
01:10:10.570 --> 01:10:13.172
The outcast attacked
a demon ship.

1313
01:10:13.308 --> 01:10:15.243
bringing death
to our people.

1314
01:10:16.207 --> 01:10:17.140
Even the son

1315
01:10:17.276 --> 01:10:18.642
of<i> Toruk Makto</i> .

1316
01:10:20.515 --> 01:10:21.977
Dad. they can't blame
Payakan for that.

1317
01:10:22.113 --> 01:10:23.047
Not now.

1318
01:10:23.183 --> 01:10:24.681
[matriarch rumbling]

1319
01:10:29.325 --> 01:10:32.018
She says he continues
to disrupt.

1320
01:10:33.087 --> 01:10:35.494
spreading bad ideas
among our young.

1321
01:10:36.427 --> 01:10:37.559
[matriarch rumbling]

1322
01:10:37.694 --> 01:10:39.463
-It's bullshit.
-It's not true.

1323
01:10:39.599 --> 01:10:40.867
[Tonowari]
She says he will only

1324
01:10:41.002 --> 01:10:42.767
bring more death.

1325
01:10:43.169 --> 01:10:44.100
Hey. why don't you

1326
01:10:44.236 --> 01:10:45.572
say something?

1327
01:10:46.241 --> 01:10:48.100
Just say something.
Please.

1328
01:10:49.141 --> 01:10:51.477
[rumbling]

1329
01:10:53.873 --> 01:10:55.914
She says the outcast

1330
01:10:56.049 --> 01:10:57.146
may not stay in

1331
01:10:57.282 --> 01:10:58.249
these waters.

1332
01:10:58.385 --> 01:10:59.083
-He must go far...
-No.

1333
01:10:59.218 --> 01:11:00.017
...where his Song

1334
01:11:00.152 --> 01:11:01.719
cannot be heard.

1335
01:11:02.121 --> 01:11:03.687
Exiled for life.

1336
01:11:06.158 --> 01:11:07.394
That's not fair.

1337
01:11:09.833 --> 01:11:10.760
It is decided.

1338
01:11:12.132 --> 01:11:13.697
[Payakan singing]

1339
01:11:16.234 --> 01:11:18.306
No! Payakan!

1340
01:11:19.974 --> 01:11:21.139
Brother! Please.

1341
01:11:21.275 --> 01:11:23.234
-No. Payakan!
-No.

1342
01:11:23.703 --> 01:11:24.440
[Lo'ak] Brother!

1343
01:11:24.575 --> 01:11:29.240
[Payakan moaning. whistling]

1344
01:11:31.187 --> 01:11:32.753
This is...
This is wrong!

1345
01:11:32.889 --> 01:11:34.388
This is wrong!

1346
01:11:35.220 --> 01:11:36.020
You do not

1347
01:11:36.155 --> 01:11:37.190
speak here.

1348
01:11:37.325 --> 01:11:38.949
No.
Payakan fought for us.

1349
01:11:39.085 --> 01:11:40.458
-He fought for us.
-Lo'ak.

1350
01:11:40.593 --> 01:11:41.955
He saved
your daughter's life.

1351
01:11:42.091 --> 01:11:43.329
-This is council.
-He saved her life!

1352
01:11:43.464 --> 01:11:45.131
-You do not speak.
-He defends us.

1353
01:11:45.267 --> 01:11:46.429
-This is council.
-Lo'ak.

1354
01:11:46.565 --> 01:11:47.827
The elders
have spoken.

1355
01:11:47.963 --> 01:11:49.462
The<i> tulkun</i> are being hunted.

1356
01:11:49.598 --> 01:11:50.503
They're dying.

1357
01:11:51.139 --> 01:11:52.496
Lo'ak. that's enough.

1358
01:11:52.632 --> 01:11:53.603
No!

1359
01:11:53.739 --> 01:11:54.999
-Lo'ak speaks the truth!
-No. Tsireya.

1360
01:11:55.134 --> 01:11:56.210
-No!
-[Tonowari] Daughter!

1361
01:11:56.346 --> 01:11:57.768
-Payakan is a warrior!
-Tsireya.

1362
01:11:57.903 --> 01:11:59.103
He fought for us.

1363
01:11:59.239 --> 01:12:01.441
-More than you. Or you.
-[clamoring]

1364
01:12:01.776 --> 01:12:03.043
More than any of you!

1365
01:12:03.178 --> 01:12:04.047
-He fought for us!
-[Tonowari] Sit down!

1366
01:12:04.182 --> 01:12:05.618
Lo'ak.

1367
01:12:05.754 --> 01:12:07.451
--Take him from here!
-You do not speak here. boy.

1368
01:12:07.586 --> 01:12:08.712
-Make a hole.
-[Kiri] Dad!

1369
01:12:08.848 --> 01:12:09.815
Listen to him!

1370
01:12:09.951 --> 01:12:10.921
[Tonowari] We are in council!

1371
01:12:11.390 --> 01:12:12.424
The elders have spoken.

1372
01:12:12.559 --> 01:12:14.725
-[shouts]
-What are you doing?

1373
01:12:16.297 --> 01:12:17.656
You never stand up for me!

1374
01:12:18.225 --> 01:12:19.763
-[Tonowari] Be seated.
-Come with me.

1375
01:12:21.468 --> 01:12:23.197
[Tonowari] Council continues.

1376
01:12:23.666 --> 01:12:25.668
[breathing heavily]

1377
01:12:25.804 --> 01:12:28.071
We're at war.
You understand that?

1378
01:12:28.473 --> 01:12:29.976
If you disobey orders.

1379
01:12:30.111 --> 01:12:32.976
people get killed.

1380
01:12:33.111 --> 01:12:35.149
With Spider here. we're trying
to keep a low profile.

1381
01:12:35.285 --> 01:12:36.843
But that rogue
is out there.

1382
01:12:36.978 --> 01:12:38.310
He's stirring up
the young bulls.

1383
01:12:38.445 --> 01:12:40.454
He was going to bring
the whole RDA down on us.

1384
01:12:41.815 --> 01:12:43.015
You want him gone.

1385
01:12:43.150 --> 01:12:44.525
That's why
you didn't say anything.

1386
01:12:45.061 --> 01:12:46.450
He's a loose cannon.

1387
01:12:46.585 --> 01:12:48.292
He's just like you.
In fact. if you hadn't gone

1388
01:12:48.428 --> 01:12:49.494
to him in the first place.

1389
01:12:49.630 --> 01:12:50.892
if you hadn't
disobeyed orders.

1390
01:12:51.027 --> 01:12:52.257
then your brother
would still be...

1391
01:12:54.762 --> 01:12:55.801
[breathes shakily]

1392
01:12:56.203 --> 01:12:58.604
[breathes shakily]

1393
01:12:59.240 --> 01:13:00.907
That wasn't my fault.

1394
01:13:01.042 --> 01:13:02.267
Dad. that...

1395
01:13:04.278 --> 01:13:06.337
That's not my fault!

1396
01:13:07.817 --> 01:13:09.978
[crying]

1397
01:13:10.413 --> 01:13:11.452
Lo'ak.

1398
01:13:16.058 --> 01:13:17.282
[breathes shakily]

1399
01:13:28.027 --> 01:13:30.064
[sighs] Go to him. Jake.

1400
01:13:34.200 --> 01:13:36.169
Or you will lose
another son.

1401
01:13:39.480 --> 01:13:41.449
I've got nothing
to say to him.

1402
01:13:43.878 --> 01:13:45.420
Do not blame Lo'ak.

1403
01:13:48.250 --> 01:13:50.289
You said you could
protect this family.

1404
01:13:50.424 --> 01:13:52.053
That.
you could do.

1405
01:13:53.089 --> 01:13:54.787
Yeah. I thought
we would be safe here.

1406
01:13:54.922 --> 01:13:57.289
Our son is dead. Jake.

1407
01:13:57.890 --> 01:13:59.291
I was wrong!

1408
01:14:01.194 --> 01:14:02.336
What do you
want me to say?

1409
01:14:02.472 --> 01:14:03.565
That every decision
that I made

1410
01:14:03.701 --> 01:14:05.099
for this family is wrong?

1411
01:14:05.899 --> 01:14:07.398
I killed our son?

1412
01:14:12.581 --> 01:14:15.109
And still we are here
in this place.

1413
01:14:15.745 --> 01:14:17.650
hiding this pink skin.

1414
01:14:19.054 --> 01:14:19.987
this alien.

1415
01:14:20.122 --> 01:14:21.212
If I had to choose

1416
01:14:21.348 --> 01:14:23.850
between my family
and a pink skin.

1417
01:14:24.319 --> 01:14:26.653
I would kill him
right now. [inhales sharply]

1418
01:14:26.788 --> 01:14:28.328
Stop. stop. stop.

1419
01:14:28.464 --> 01:14:29.921
We're not doing this.
Look.

1420
01:14:30.056 --> 01:14:31.391
We're not doing this.

1421
01:14:31.793 --> 01:14:33.127
You already chose

1422
01:14:33.262 --> 01:14:35.562
between your family
and a pink skin once.

1423
01:14:35.697 --> 01:14:37.296
remember?

1424
01:14:40.706 --> 01:14:43.568
You cannot live
like this. baby.

1425
01:14:43.704 --> 01:14:45.304
In hate.

1426
01:14:46.515 --> 01:14:49.082
I hate them. Jake.
I hate them.

1427
01:14:49.217 --> 01:14:50.885
[breathes heavily]

1428
01:14:51.020 --> 01:14:52.144
I hate them.

1429
01:14:52.279 --> 01:14:54.745
I hate their
pink little hands.

1430
01:14:55.448 --> 01:14:58.449
I hate the insanity
in their minds.

1431
01:15:01.591 --> 01:15:02.695
I'm a human.

1432
01:15:03.229 --> 01:15:04.489
Inside.

1433
01:15:04.891 --> 01:15:06.193
You hate me?

1434
01:15:08.131 --> 01:15:10.236
I'll always be an alien
to you. won't I?

1435
01:15:10.772 --> 01:15:13.200
Doesn't matter how long
I live in this skin.

1436
01:15:15.278 --> 01:15:16.610
Do you hate your children?

1437
01:15:18.445 --> 01:15:20.438
With their alien hands?

1438
01:15:21.951 --> 01:15:23.177
No.

1439
01:15:23.844 --> 01:15:25.085
Are you ashamed

1440
01:15:25.554 --> 01:15:26.914
every time
they make a mistake.

1441
01:15:27.050 --> 01:15:28.380
every time
they're different?

1442
01:15:30.225 --> 01:15:31.249
That's because of

1443
01:15:31.384 --> 01:15:33.319
the human
inside them. right?

1444
01:15:35.657 --> 01:15:36.696
Yes.

1445
01:15:37.431 --> 01:15:39.633
[breathing shakily]

1446
01:15:46.703 --> 01:15:48.202
[breathes deeply]

1447
01:15:55.117 --> 01:15:56.408
I'm sorry. baby.

1448
01:15:57.185 --> 01:15:58.509
I'm sorry.

1449
01:15:59.220 --> 01:16:00.445
I'm sorry.

1450
01:16:03.592 --> 01:16:06.990
We have to stand strong
right now.

1451
01:16:08.320 --> 01:16:10.488
This family is our fortress.

1452
01:16:17.163 --> 01:16:19.398
[breathing heavily]

1453
01:16:33.284 --> 01:16:35.516
<i> The People say</i>
<i> that when you touch steel.</i>

1454
01:16:36.252 --> 01:16:38.252
<i> its poison</i>
<i> seeps into your heart.</i>

1455
01:16:40.021 --> 01:16:42.256
[breathing shakily]

1456
01:16:54.542 --> 01:16:56.776
[yells. breathing heavily]

1457
01:17:00.742 --> 01:17:02.573
[crying]

1458
01:17:03.613 --> 01:17:04.652
Lo'ak!

1459
01:17:05.549 --> 01:17:06.481
Brother.

1460
01:17:06.616 --> 01:17:07.655
Lo'ak.

1461
01:17:12.891 --> 01:17:14.953
Stay in this life.
Brother.

1462
01:17:15.088 --> 01:17:17.031
[breathes heavily]

1463
01:17:17.166 --> 01:17:18.461
We need you.

1464
01:17:18.596 --> 01:17:19.960
We love you.

1465
01:17:20.096 --> 01:17:21.660
You have greatness
in you.

1466
01:17:21.796 --> 01:17:23.429
[crying]

1467
01:17:34.876 --> 01:17:36.244
[Kiri sighs]

1468
01:17:37.479 --> 01:17:40.512
The strength of the
ancestors is here.

1469
01:17:44.756 --> 01:17:46.254
A bow can be fixed.

1470
01:17:51.597 --> 01:17:54.201
[breathes deeply]

1471
01:17:54.336 --> 01:17:57.397
[groans. strains]

1472
01:18:03.542 --> 01:18:04.778
Good. Good.

1473
01:18:13.651 --> 01:18:15.217
Moment of truth.

1474
01:18:19.921 --> 01:18:21.356
[whistles]

1475
01:18:21.758 --> 01:18:24.457
Whoa. [chuckles]

1476
01:18:26.993 --> 01:18:28.098
Go.

1477
01:18:31.673 --> 01:18:33.664
-[chuckles]
-You feel her?

1478
01:18:34.100 --> 01:18:35.439
Hell yeah.

1479
01:18:35.574 --> 01:18:36.843
I got fins.

1480
01:18:37.679 --> 01:18:39.275
[chuckling]
Yeah. you do.

1481
01:18:39.811 --> 01:18:42.611
-Whoo!
-Whoo!

1482
01:18:42.746 --> 01:18:44.576
Go. Monkey Boy!

1483
01:18:55.923 --> 01:18:57.490
Whoo!

1484
01:19:02.898 --> 01:19:04.227
You. Face down!

1485
01:19:04.363 --> 01:19:05.597
Eyes on the ground.

1486
01:19:06.706 --> 01:19:07.966
Stay calm. my people.

1487
01:19:08.101 --> 01:19:09.339
Stay calm.

1488
01:19:09.741 --> 01:19:11.405
[screams. groans]

1489
01:19:11.874 --> 01:19:13.704
Spider. Huh?

1490
01:19:13.839 --> 01:19:15.309
I think we're wasting
our time. Colonel.

1491
01:19:15.445 --> 01:19:17.544
-They don't know anything.
-Oh. they know.

1492
01:19:18.180 --> 01:19:19.754
They're just not talking.

1493
01:19:21.281 --> 01:19:23.048
We got one more play.

1494
01:19:23.183 --> 01:19:24.655
but it's radical.

1495
01:19:24.791 --> 01:19:27.025
[♪ tense music plays]

1496
01:19:46.207 --> 01:19:48.244
[breathing heavily]

1497
01:20:01.963 --> 01:20:03.358
-[Mangkwan ululating]
-[grunts]

1498
01:20:04.497 --> 01:20:06.064
[grunts]

1499
01:20:07.563 --> 01:20:09.695
Hey. you remember me.
don't you? [groans]

1500
01:20:10.331 --> 01:20:12.164
[grunts] Whoa. whoa. whoa.

1501
01:20:12.300 --> 01:20:13.900
-Mine!
-Just relax.

1502
01:20:14.035 --> 01:20:16.135
-Get him up.
-I brought something
for your<i> Tsahik</i> .

1503
01:20:16.671 --> 01:20:19.171
-You take me to your<i> Tsahì</i> --
-Move!

1504
01:20:19.307 --> 01:20:20.809
-Hey. hey!
-Move!

1505
01:20:20.945 --> 01:20:22.177
No need to do that.

1506
01:20:22.313 --> 01:20:24.412
-I got my eye on you.
-Keep going.

1507
01:20:26.216 --> 01:20:28.449
[Mangkwan chanting. whooping]

1508
01:20:31.321 --> 01:20:33.085
-[Quaritch grunts]
-[horn blowing]

1509
01:20:33.221 --> 01:20:34.455
[Mangkwan warrior] Move!

1510
01:20:42.096 --> 01:20:42.997
<i> Tsahik.</i>

1511
01:20:43.132 --> 01:20:45.004
What is he doing here?

1512
01:20:48.172 --> 01:20:49.404
[Mangkwan warrior 2]<i> Tsahik.</i>

1513
01:20:50.741 --> 01:20:52.044
[grunts]

1514
01:21:05.752 --> 01:21:08.159
I'll get you as many
as you want.

1515
01:21:11.127 --> 01:21:13.362
[warriors snarling]

1516
01:21:18.565 --> 01:21:21.506
What is your name.
Sky Man?

1517
01:21:21.641 --> 01:21:23.009
Quaritch.

1518
01:21:23.975 --> 01:21:26.276
Colonel Miles Quaritch.

1519
01:21:28.946 --> 01:21:29.976
[Varang] Hmm.

1520
01:21:30.845 --> 01:21:33.516
You touch me with that
thing again. I'll kill you.

1521
01:21:34.018 --> 01:21:36.389
You will kill no one.

1522
01:21:36.524 --> 01:21:37.655
[chuckling]

1523
01:21:38.024 --> 01:21:40.789
Lady. I'm gonna
beg to differ.

1524
01:21:41.292 --> 01:21:42.523
-Drop him.
-[gunshot echoes]

1525
01:21:45.528 --> 01:21:48.562
-[hisses]
-[Mangkwan clamoring]

1526
01:22:06.555 --> 01:22:07.713
Good trick...

1527
01:22:09.557 --> 01:22:10.584
Quaritch.

1528
01:22:12.023 --> 01:22:13.718
You're next. cupcake.

1529
01:22:13.854 --> 01:22:16.425
So think careful
about what you want to do.

1530
01:22:19.467 --> 01:22:20.495
Come.

1531
01:22:21.967 --> 01:22:24.103
We will talk inside.

1532
01:22:30.175 --> 01:22:32.177
What are you doing.
boss?

1533
01:22:44.724 --> 01:22:46.026
[chuckles]

1534
01:22:48.859 --> 01:22:50.096
Cozy.

1535
01:22:52.864 --> 01:22:54.232
See. thing is...

1536
01:22:56.332 --> 01:22:58.236
everybody's lying
to me.

1537
01:23:04.646 --> 01:23:05.672
They say that

1538
01:23:07.412 --> 01:23:10.182
you can make a stone
speak the truth.

1539
01:23:10.651 --> 01:23:11.884
You seek a man.

1540
01:23:12.020 --> 01:23:14.219
the other Sky Man
like you.

1541
01:23:14.952 --> 01:23:16.386
Not like me.

1542
01:23:17.419 --> 01:23:18.685
No.
he's a traitor.

1543
01:23:20.256 --> 01:23:21.725
Well. then he must die.

1544
01:23:21.860 --> 01:23:23.096
[chuckles]

1545
01:23:24.197 --> 01:23:26.759
Varang can help you
find this man.

1546
01:23:28.365 --> 01:23:30.268
And the other
you seek.

1547
01:23:32.771 --> 01:23:34.008
This...

1548
01:23:34.577 --> 01:23:35.608
air breather.

1549
01:23:35.744 --> 01:23:36.769
[Quaritch chuckles]

1550
01:23:41.341 --> 01:23:42.583
[Varang] First.

1551
01:23:42.718 --> 01:23:44.416
I must see your soul.

1552
01:23:44.552 --> 01:23:45.584
[groans]

1553
01:23:45.719 --> 01:23:47.021
Be still.

1554
01:23:48.724 --> 01:23:49.749
[echoing] Be still.

1555
01:23:53.187 --> 01:23:54.754
[blows]

1556
01:23:55.895 --> 01:23:57.361
[grunts] Whoa.

1557
01:23:58.459 --> 01:24:00.260
[chuckles] Whoa. Whoa.

1558
01:24:00.396 --> 01:24:01.996
[♪ eerie music plays]

1559
01:24:02.131 --> 01:24:03.466
[Quaritch] Whoa.

1560
01:24:13.078 --> 01:24:15.049
That's some strong shit.

1561
01:24:50.783 --> 01:24:52.009
This...

1562
01:24:53.519 --> 01:24:56.288
is the only pure thing
in this world. [echoes]

1563
01:24:57.659 --> 01:24:58.655
[chuckles]

1564
01:24:59.458 --> 01:25:01.793
The fire came
from the mountain

1565
01:25:01.928 --> 01:25:03.295
when I was little.

1566
01:25:04.999 --> 01:25:07.101
[echoing] Burned our forest.

1567
01:25:08.837 --> 01:25:10.599
It took everything.

1568
01:25:15.239 --> 01:25:18.442
My people were starving.

1569
01:25:19.045 --> 01:25:21.247
They cried for help.

1570
01:25:23.819 --> 01:25:27.011
But Eywa did not come.

1571
01:25:29.352 --> 01:25:32.555
So I went to the fire.

1572
01:25:35.259 --> 01:25:38.231
And I learned its way.

1573
01:25:43.662 --> 01:25:46.305
I am the fire.

1574
01:25:48.677 --> 01:25:50.909
By my hand.

1575
01:25:51.044 --> 01:25:53.546
my people grow strong.

1576
01:25:54.049 --> 01:25:56.914
We do not lie down
and die

1577
01:25:57.049 --> 01:25:58.447
just because Eywa

1578
01:25:58.583 --> 01:26:00.385
-turns her back on us.
-[grunts]

1579
01:26:02.122 --> 01:26:05.225
We turn our back
on Eywa.

1580
01:26:06.795 --> 01:26:08.492
a weak mother

1581
01:26:09.622 --> 01:26:11.161
for weak children.

1582
01:26:11.296 --> 01:26:13.057
[Quaritch breathes heavily]

1583
01:26:13.901 --> 01:26:16.794
We do not suck

1584
01:26:16.929 --> 01:26:19.635
on the breast
of weakness.

1585
01:26:23.942 --> 01:26:26.037
Now...

1586
01:26:28.013 --> 01:26:29.939
only true words

1587
01:26:30.075 --> 01:26:32.186
will come
from your tongue.

1588
01:26:33.886 --> 01:26:35.112
Mmm.

1589
01:26:36.922 --> 01:26:38.315
[sighs]

1590
01:26:38.751 --> 01:26:40.458
You have a strong heart.

1591
01:26:41.421 --> 01:26:42.526
No fear.

1592
01:26:43.127 --> 01:26:44.627
[grunts] Ow.

1593
01:26:45.295 --> 01:26:46.598
[chuckles] Ow.

1594
01:26:46.967 --> 01:26:48.101
That wasn't cool.

1595
01:26:48.237 --> 01:26:50.901
I will eat
your heart. Quaritch.

1596
01:26:51.037 --> 01:26:53.372
Oh. [laughing]

1597
01:26:56.673 --> 01:27:00.247
But first.
you will answer me.

1598
01:27:03.918 --> 01:27:06.011
