'Cause I'm starving.

2393
02:11:54.000 --> 02:11:55.302
You were right.

2394
02:12:00.370 --> 02:12:02.045
It has to be done.

2395
02:12:03.877 --> 02:12:05.081
Jake.

2396
02:12:05.747 --> 02:12:06.778
[sighs]

2397
02:12:07.147 --> 02:12:09.085
He saved your life.

2398
02:12:17.057 --> 02:12:18.292
[breathes shakily]

2399
02:12:20.028 --> 02:12:22.065
This is the only way.

2400
02:12:23.868 --> 02:12:26.102
[♪ tense music playing]

2401
02:12:34.546 --> 02:12:35.771
Spider...

2402
02:12:37.582 --> 02:12:38.609
Come here.

2403
02:12:45.757 --> 02:12:46.991
What's
going on?

2404
02:12:49.990 --> 02:12:51.259
What is it?

2405
02:12:51.960 --> 02:12:53.393
Just come with me.

2406
02:12:55.766 --> 02:12:57.067
Come on. Let's go.

2407
02:12:59.705 --> 02:13:01.500
[breathing heavily]

2408
02:13:06.475 --> 02:13:08.170
Hey. stop for a second.
I gotta take a leak.

2409
02:13:08.305 --> 02:13:10.080
Just stay close.

2410
02:13:18.955 --> 02:13:20.288
Where are we going?

2411
02:13:20.790 --> 02:13:22.092
Be quiet.

2412
02:13:27.425 --> 02:13:29.594
[breathing heavily]

2413
02:13:37.206 --> 02:13:39.406
So. is this.
like. a talk?

2414
02:13:50.819 --> 02:13:51.917
[sighs]

2415
02:13:52.052 --> 02:13:52.919
Come here.

2416
02:13:53.054 --> 02:13:54.553
Come on.
Come on.

2417
02:13:55.659 --> 02:13:56.621
Go.

2418
02:13:58.224 --> 02:13:59.591
This'll work.

2419
02:14:00.763 --> 02:14:01.989
Kneel.

2420
02:14:02.534 --> 02:14:03.634
Kneel.

2421
02:14:03.770 --> 02:14:04.700
-No.
-Kneel down.

2422
02:14:04.835 --> 02:14:06.402
[Spider grunting]

2423
02:14:06.538 --> 02:14:08.033
Please.

2424
02:14:08.168 --> 02:14:09.801
Jake. please stop.

2425
02:14:10.270 --> 02:14:12.604
Eyes front. Don't move.

2426
02:14:13.072 --> 02:14:14.240
Please.

2427
02:14:14.375 --> 02:14:15.538
you don't have
to do this.

2428
02:14:15.673 --> 02:14:17.776
-Shh!
-[breathes heavily]

2429
02:14:17.912 --> 02:14:19.083
Please.

2430
02:14:19.885 --> 02:14:21.613
Great Mother. are you here?

2431
02:14:23.385 --> 02:14:25.122
[Spider] You don't
have to do this.

2432
02:14:25.790 --> 02:14:26.757
Guide my hand.

2433
02:14:26.893 --> 02:14:27.756
[Spider] Please don't do this.

2434
02:14:27.891 --> 02:14:29.053
Give me strength.

2435
02:14:29.188 --> 02:14:30.660
Just stop.

2436
02:14:30.796 --> 02:14:32.694
Please stop. Please.

2437
02:14:33.097 --> 02:14:34.521
-Don't look at me.
-Please.

2438
02:14:34.656 --> 02:14:35.990
Don't look at me.

2439
02:14:36.933 --> 02:14:38.168
[inhales sharply]

2440
02:14:38.703 --> 02:14:39.831
Forgive me. Son.

2441
02:14:40.200 --> 02:14:41.134
I'll be good.

2442
02:14:41.269 --> 02:14:42.873
May your spirit go to Eywa.

2443
02:14:43.008 --> 02:14:44.135
-I promise.
-May your body

2444
02:14:44.271 --> 02:14:45.872
return to the forest...

2445
02:14:46.007 --> 02:14:47.071
[sniffles]

2446
02:14:47.206 --> 02:14:48.341
Please. Dad.

2447
02:14:48.477 --> 02:14:50.007
...to preserve
the Great Balance.

2448
02:14:50.643 --> 02:14:52.813
May the ancestors
welcome you.

2449
02:14:52.948 --> 02:14:55.185
[sobbing]

2450
02:15:05.326 --> 02:15:06.658
[exhales sharply. exclaims]

2451
02:15:07.764 --> 02:15:08.760
Please.

2452
02:15:09.563 --> 02:15:11.968
May the ancestors
hold you.

2453
02:15:12.103 --> 02:15:14.270
May they sing
your Song.

2454
02:15:15.339 --> 02:15:17.438
I know I have to go
to Eywa now.

2455
02:15:18.743 --> 02:15:20.177
It's okay.

2456
02:15:20.909 --> 02:15:22.146
But...

2457
02:15:23.209 --> 02:15:24.445
Do you...

2458
02:15:25.246 --> 02:15:27.008
Do you still love me?

2459
02:15:28.787 --> 02:15:30.451
With all my heart.

2460
02:15:34.422 --> 02:15:36.655
[♪ emotional music playing]

2461
02:15:39.799 --> 02:15:42.023
[both breathing shakily]

2462
02:15:51.940 --> 02:15:53.177
[grunts]

2463
02:15:54.075 --> 02:15:56.103
[Spider panting]

2464
02:15:58.114 --> 02:15:59.612
[breathing shakily]

2465
02:16:14.233 --> 02:16:16.123
[crying]<i> Ma Jake</i> .<i> Ma Jake</i> .

2466
02:16:27.570 --> 02:16:29.180
I See you.

2467
02:16:36.179 --> 02:16:38.922
Whatever happens.
it won't be this way.

2468
02:16:39.057 --> 02:16:40.981
[Neytiri breathing heavily]

2469
02:16:41.116 --> 02:16:43.557
Then we will find
another way.

2470
02:16:48.133 --> 02:16:50.366
[♪ hopeful music playing]

2471
02:16:59.906 --> 02:17:01.511
[Lo'ak]<i> My dad knew</i>
<i> in his heart</i>

2472
02:17:01.880 --> 02:17:02.712
<i> there was only</i>

2473
02:17:02.848 --> 02:17:05.216
<i> ever one path.</i>

2474
02:17:08.415 --> 02:17:10.045
[Jake breathes shakily]

2475
02:17:11.854 --> 02:17:14.181
[Lo'ak]<i> No matter</i>
<i> how you imagine yourself.</i>

2476
02:17:14.893 --> 02:17:16.185
<i> as a father.</i>

2477
02:17:16.620 --> 02:17:17.756
<i> as a husband.</i>

2478
02:17:18.623 --> 02:17:19.760
<i> sooner or later.</i>

2479
02:17:20.262 --> 02:17:21.589
<i> you're back on it.</i>

2480
02:17:22.325 --> 02:17:24.565
-[Toruk breathing heavily]
-[Jake exhales deeply]

2481
02:17:37.277 --> 02:17:39.481
[Toruk rumbling]

2482
02:17:41.051 --> 02:17:42.651
Hello. old friend.

2483
02:17:42.787 --> 02:17:44.387
[sighs]

2484
02:17:45.223 --> 02:17:47.258
[Lo'ak] Toruk<i> loved my father.</i>

2485
02:17:48.519 --> 02:17:49.790
[screeches]

2486
02:17:49.925 --> 02:17:51.925
[Lo'ak]<i> It knew they were</i>
<i> greater together.</i>

2487
02:17:52.361 --> 02:17:53.594
<i> That when they flew.</i>

2488
02:17:54.462 --> 02:17:56.124
<i> there would be blood.</i>

2489
02:17:57.628 --> 02:17:59.428
[Toruk screeches]

2490
02:17:59.564 --> 02:18:00.700
He is coming.

2491
02:18:02.107 --> 02:18:04.341
[♪ dramatic music plays]

2492
02:18:05.107 --> 02:18:07.172
[clan whooping]

2493
02:18:07.307 --> 02:18:09.203
[speaking Na'vi]

2494
02:18:20.088 --> 02:18:22.755
[roars]

2495
02:18:25.194 --> 02:18:26.730
<i> Toruk Makto!</i>

2496
02:18:26.866 --> 02:18:28.090
[clan grunts]

2497
02:18:30.068 --> 02:18:31.625
No. no. no. Just...

2498
02:18:31.761 --> 02:18:33.529
Please. stand.

2499
02:18:33.664 --> 02:18:35.703
Stand up. Please.

2500
02:18:36.239 --> 02:18:37.638
-Baby.
-Jake.

2501
02:18:38.768 --> 02:18:40.370
Please. It's okay.

2502
02:18:40.505 --> 02:18:41.543
It's okay.

2503
02:18:43.573 --> 02:18:44.941
Go now

2504
02:18:45.076 --> 02:18:46.574
to all the clans
within a day's ride

2505
02:18:46.709 --> 02:18:47.978
and tell 'em...

2506
02:18:48.787 --> 02:18:49.919
[sighs]

2507
02:18:50.555 --> 02:18:53.016
Tell 'em<i> Toruk Makto</i>
calls to them.

2508
02:18:54.818 --> 02:18:56.525
And you tell 'em...

2509
02:18:58.029 --> 02:18:59.627
the day has come.

2510
02:19:08.532 --> 02:19:09.498
[shouts]

2511
02:19:09.633 --> 02:19:11.298
[ululating]

2512
02:19:35.065 --> 02:19:36.697
[cheering]

2513
02:19:39.370 --> 02:19:41.070
[Lo'ak]<i> And so it came to pass</i>

2514
02:19:41.606 --> 02:19:43.372
<i> that</i> Toruk Makto
<i> returned.</i>

2515
02:19:43.508 --> 02:19:45.568
<i> My father united</i>
<i> the clans</i>

2516
02:19:45.703 --> 02:19:46.839
<i> once again.</i>

2517
02:19:47.776 --> 02:19:49.712
<i> He made the</i>
<i> great speeches.</i>

2518
02:19:50.115 --> 02:19:51.112
Many arrows together

2519
02:19:51.247 --> 02:19:53.516
cannot be broken.

2520
02:19:55.714 --> 02:19:57.711
We cannot be broken!

2521
02:19:57.846 --> 02:19:59.481
[cheering]

2522
02:20:00.050 --> 02:20:01.689
[♪ inspirational music plays]

2523
02:20:05.422 --> 02:20:08.124
[Lo'ak]<i> But he knew</i>
<i> that it wasn't enough.</i>

2524
02:20:25.951 --> 02:20:27.675
Great Matriarch.

2525
02:20:27.810 --> 02:20:29.310
wise elders.

2526
02:20:30.948 --> 02:20:32.522
the Sky People are coming.

2527
02:20:33.255 --> 02:20:34.550
Here. today.

2528
02:20:34.685 --> 02:20:35.823
Right now.

2529
02:20:36.626 --> 02:20:38.594
To kill our<i> tulkun</i> families.

2530
02:20:39.195 --> 02:20:40.431
I beg you.

2531
02:20:41.297 --> 02:20:42.697
fight with us.

2532
02:20:46.862 --> 02:20:48.505
[rumbles]

2533
02:20:50.841 --> 02:20:53.841
She says.
"We respect<i> Toruk Makto</i> .

2534
02:20:54.610 --> 02:20:56.645
but our ways
are ancient."

2535
02:20:57.213 --> 02:20:59.010
[rumbles]

2536
02:21:00.777 --> 02:21:02.112
"We believe

2537
02:21:02.247 --> 02:21:04.680
that killing will only
bring more killing.

2538
02:21:05.183 --> 02:21:08.151
in an endless.
expanding spiral."

2539
02:21:10.722 --> 02:21:12.122
Hear my words.

2540
02:21:13.398 --> 02:21:16.133
The Sky People
will never stop.

2541
02:21:16.669 --> 02:21:19.393
Not until the last
of the<i> tulkun</i> is hunted.

2542
02:21:19.829 --> 02:21:22.066
[bellows]

2543
02:21:26.769 --> 02:21:27.709
Lo'ak.

2544
02:21:35.482 --> 02:21:36.619
[Payakan]

2545
02:21:37.847 --> 02:21:39.655
[matriarch]

2546
02:21:41.586 --> 02:21:42.724
Stop.

2547
02:21:42.860 --> 02:21:44.059
Lo'ak. what are you doing?
You can't be here.

2548
02:21:44.194 --> 02:21:45.595
Dad. wait.

2549
02:21:46.864 --> 02:21:49.466
I am Brother of<i> tulkun.</i>
I have a right to speak.

2550
02:21:49.601 --> 02:21:53.097
Lo'ak speaks the truth.
You must listen.

2551
02:21:53.499 --> 02:21:54.528
Tsireya.

2552
02:21:54.897 --> 02:21:56.540
[rumbles]

2553
02:21:59.006 --> 02:22:01.712
She says.
"His Brother is outcast."

2554
02:22:02.281 --> 02:22:04.977
You have no standing here.

2555
02:22:06.745 --> 02:22:08.376
If he is outcast.

2556
02:22:09.011 --> 02:22:10.752
then I am outcast.

2557
02:22:11.717 --> 02:22:13.716
And I am outcast.

2558
02:22:13.851 --> 02:22:15.319
Daughter. silence.

2559
02:22:15.455 --> 02:22:16.291
No.

2560
02:22:16.660 --> 02:22:18.760
You will never
see me again.

2561
02:22:20.632 --> 02:22:23.063
And I and my Brother
are outcast.

2562
02:22:23.199 --> 02:22:24.594
Aonung.

2563
02:22:24.729 --> 02:22:26.794
And we are

2564
02:22:26.930 --> 02:22:28.099
also outcast.

2565
02:22:34.670 --> 02:22:37.075
-[Neytiri breathes shakily]
-[rumbles. clicks]

2566
02:22:40.243 --> 02:22:43.114
She says.
"You may speak."

2567
02:22:47.116 --> 02:22:48.382
[Lo'ak] Hear my words.

2568
02:22:48.518 --> 02:22:50.719
My Brother returned
to his birth clan

2569
02:22:50.854 --> 02:22:51.995
to defend them.

2570
02:22:52.530 --> 02:22:54.691
but his clan
was wiped out

2571
02:22:54.827 --> 02:22:56.328
by the demon ships.

2572
02:22:56.697 --> 02:22:58.461
Only Ta'nok survived.

2573
02:22:58.864 --> 02:23:00.527
because she fought back.

2574
02:23:01.833 --> 02:23:02.973
Come forward.

2575
02:23:03.409 --> 02:23:05.202
[♪ mournful music playing]

2576
02:23:19.783 --> 02:23:21.317
[sighs]

2577
02:23:23.095 --> 02:23:25.193
[exhales]

2578
02:23:25.329 --> 02:23:27.158
[Ta'nok wails]

2579
02:23:30.135 --> 02:23:31.225
Ta'nok says.

2580
02:23:31.360 --> 02:23:35.067
"I speak
for the dead mothers

2581
02:23:35.703 --> 02:23:36.706
and the dead calves."

2582
02:23:37.175 --> 02:23:38.741
[Ta'nok moaning]

2583
02:23:42.440 --> 02:23:45.440
"I speak for my people
and all our Songs."

2584
02:23:46.008 --> 02:23:47.742
[wailing]

2585
02:23:47.877 --> 02:23:49.147
"Gone.

2586
02:23:50.584 --> 02:23:51.754
Forever."

2587
02:23:53.752 --> 02:23:56.554
[wailing]

2588
02:23:56.689 --> 02:23:57.859
She says.

2589
02:23:57.994 --> 02:24:00.664
"I am the last.
The blind witness to our end."

2590
02:24:02.359 --> 02:24:04.998
-[Ta'nok wails]
-[sniffles. sighs]

2591
02:24:07.172 --> 02:24:08.329
Ta'nok says.

2592
02:24:08.464 --> 02:24:10.566
"The<i> tulkun</i> way
must change.

2593
02:24:10.969 --> 02:24:13.072
Payakan shows our path."

2594
02:24:13.706 --> 02:24:15.437
[rumbling]

2595
02:24:17.072 --> 02:24:19.276
[bellows]

2596
02:24:20.647 --> 02:24:22.413
"We must fight."

2597
02:24:22.782 --> 02:24:24.281
We must fight!

2598
02:24:26.257 --> 02:24:28.153
[rumbling]

2599
02:24:41.735 --> 02:24:43.235
What did she say?

2600
02:24:43.737 --> 02:24:45.335
They will decide.

2601
02:24:46.444 --> 02:24:47.601
Look at all of this.

2602
02:24:48.613 --> 02:24:50.813
I mean. there's
hundreds of 'em.

2603
02:24:51.616 --> 02:24:53.413
And look at all
these old ones.

2604
02:24:53.548 --> 02:24:55.284
And old is good.

2605
02:24:55.420 --> 02:24:57.149
They never stop growing.

2606
02:24:57.818 --> 02:24:59.415
which means more amrita.

2607
02:25:00.755 --> 02:25:01.949
And look at this mama.

2608
02:25:02.084 --> 02:25:02.884
She must be

2609
02:25:03.019 --> 02:25:04.387
100 meters.

2610
02:25:05.520 --> 02:25:06.763
You're briefing
without me.

2611
02:25:08.028 --> 02:25:09.794
An oversight.
I assume.

2612
02:25:10.163 --> 02:25:11.993
No. it was not
an oversight.

2613
02:25:12.462 --> 02:25:13.765
After your fiasco
with Sully.

2614
02:25:13.900 --> 02:25:15.267
you're done. Colonel.

2615
02:25:15.770 --> 02:25:16.736
You're confined to base

2616
02:25:16.872 --> 02:25:17.997
pending
an investigation.

2617
02:25:18.633 --> 02:25:20.469
Negative on that.
I need to roll.

2618
02:25:20.604 --> 02:25:22.807
Sully will be there.
which means that Spider

2619
02:25:22.942 --> 02:25:23.807
will be there as well.

2620
02:25:23.942 --> 02:25:25.177
Don't look at him.

2621
02:25:25.312 --> 02:25:26.106
He's one step away
from the brig himself.

2622
02:25:26.609 --> 02:25:28.046
Don't tell him
not to look at me.

2623
02:25:28.182 --> 02:25:30.147
What are you gonna do?
Call Daddy?

2624
02:25:30.283 --> 02:25:32.382
-You mean the chairman?
-That's enough.

2625
02:25:33.792 --> 02:25:36.456
I can still complete
this mission.

2626
02:25:36.591 --> 02:25:37.656
Look at you.

2627
02:25:38.192 --> 02:25:39.587
You're a disgrace
to your uniform.

2628
02:25:39.722 --> 02:25:42.557
Assuming you remember
what a uniform is.

2629
02:25:43.799 --> 02:25:45.663
You're grounded. Colonel.

2630
02:25:45.798 --> 02:25:47.199
Permanently.

2631
02:25:47.799 --> 02:25:49.867
[sighs]

2632
02:25:50.002 --> 02:25:52.237
[clan speaking Na'vi]

2633
02:26:02.382 --> 02:26:04.579
-[breathing heavily]
-Why are you here. girl?

2634
02:26:06.954 --> 02:26:08.517
To pray.<i> Tsahik</i> .

2635
02:26:11.526 --> 02:26:12.620
[pants]

2636
02:26:13.122 --> 02:26:14.457
No. child.

2637
02:26:18.164 --> 02:26:20.298
Why did you
come to us?

2638
02:26:23.208 --> 02:26:24.569
Perhaps

2639
02:26:24.938 --> 02:26:26.573
it was for this moment.

2640
02:26:26.708 --> 02:26:28.374
[inhales sharply]

2641
02:26:28.743 --> 02:26:29.672
Only a chosen one

2642
02:26:29.808 --> 02:26:31.111
may call

2643
02:26:31.714 --> 02:26:33.141
upon the Warrior Mother.

2644
02:26:33.277 --> 02:26:35.082
[inhales sharply. groans]

2645
02:26:36.518 --> 02:26:37.582
[groans]

2646
02:26:37.718 --> 02:26:39.253
<i> Tsahik.</i>

2647
02:26:39.855 --> 02:26:41.486
You're having contractions.

2648
02:26:41.888 --> 02:26:43.591
I fear we will...

2649
02:26:43.727 --> 02:26:45.251
we will not survive this.

2650
02:26:45.387 --> 02:26:48.095
[breathing shakily]

2651
02:26:50.466 --> 02:26:51.494
Kiri.

2652
02:26:54.263 --> 02:26:55.964
Hear my words.

2653
02:26:56.633 --> 02:27:00.074
If there is something
you can do.

2654
02:27:01.437 --> 02:27:03.704
then you must
do it.

2655
02:27:06.376 --> 02:27:09.512
You have
a strong heart.

2656
02:27:10.552 --> 02:27:11.580
Here.

2657
02:27:12.315 --> 02:27:13.583
I'm riding with you?

2658
02:27:14.119 --> 02:27:15.716
No. I need you here.

2659
02:27:16.558 --> 02:27:17.491
